    (W_analytic_lorentz_holomorphic Wfn n Λ)
    (Wfn.spectrum_condition n).choose_spec.1
    (W_analytic_lorentz_bv_agree Wfn n Λ)
  exact huniq z hz

/-- W_analytic extends continuously to the real boundary of the forward tube.

